Smart ITSI Predictions App for Splunk

Contributor: Greg Ainslie-Malik, gainsliemalik@splunk.com

This app is designed to provide a guided workflow for generating predictive health score sin ITSI.

Prerequesites for this app:
- Splunk Machine Learning Toolkit version 5 or above installed: https://splunkbase.splunk.com/app/2890/
